-Agahnim Dragmire <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ucorwwyn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Corwwyn</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(8/15/01 12:35:06 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Our prayers have been answered! (SEVERLY important, read</span><hr size=1> Interesting idea Agahnim, could give us an exploratory use in groups (like the way rogues' ability to open locked doors in those few areas they are needed).<br>
<br>
Mektanra, re your point 5:  If the resist situation you mention is on static mobs that are the same each spawn, then a valid point(eg Nostro in SK).   <br>
<br>
I think on static spawns that aren't named, or that have a level range the differing resists would be considered &quot;working as intended&quot;, and I personally have no problem with that in this case.  <br>
<br>
It seems to me that these range-of-levels mobs also seem to go through a cycle of around 4 or so, where each spawn gets higher, then back to lowest or something like that.  I havent given it an in-depth study or anything, but there always seems to be an eventual &quot;resister&quot;, immediately followed by a relatively very easy mob.<br>
<br>
I wonder, has anyone else found this?  ...or analyzed it in depth?  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.showMessage?topicID=545.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.emailToFriend?topicID=484.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.threadControl?topicID=484.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=484.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm10.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=484.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub23.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm1">General Discussion<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm3">Trade Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm4">Rant Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm8">Mob Dropped Spells<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm10">Class Balance & Class Bugs<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm22">Out of Mana<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm27">PVP Forum<option value="graffeswizardcompilationfrm28">The Library<option value="graffeswizardc